

   1. Download PySOS


   2. Install PostgreSQL, Python, Apache, mod_python, and PyGreSQL.


   3. Unzip pysos.tar.gz to your web server

   4. Configure Apache

<Location /your/path>
  SetHandler mod_python
  PythonHandler psphandler
  PythonDebug On
</Location>

   5. Edit config.py, changing the application paths, and the queries used to extract oferings, observedProperties, sensors, and observations


   6. Test by pointing your browser to http://your.domain/your/path/sos.py


